        <num>CCP 3827</num>
        <heading>3827.  Inability to produce person in custody</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3827.  Inability to produce person in custody
If the person in custody cannot be brought before the court, the reasons therefor shall be stated in the answer.  The hearing may proceed as if he had been produced.</p>
        </content>
